WEBVTT

00:00:11.105 --> 00:00:13.025
Since when did we hire this baker?

00:00:13.105 --> 00:00:14.545
Are you a "hit and run" guy?

00:00:14.625 --> 00:00:16.225
It was just
a "friends with benefits" thing.

00:00:16.305 --> 00:00:18.105
-Are you hungry?
-Huh? Hungry for what?

00:00:18.185 --> 00:00:19.825
Whoa, easy! You’ll get drunk.

00:00:19.905 --> 00:00:21.425
I can handle this much.

00:00:24.265 --> 00:00:26.825
and finally--

00:00:28.145 --> 00:00:29.025
200 drinks.

00:00:32.385 --> 00:00:34.105
I don’t sleep with just anyone.

00:00:34.185 --> 00:00:36.025
From now on, you have to call me…

00:00:36.105 --> 00:00:37.065
Pi Doc.

00:00:38.185 --> 00:00:39.345
Nong Sailom.

00:00:39.425 --> 00:00:41.025
Okay, Pi Doc.

00:01:49.025 --> 00:01:50.145
Here’s a receipt.

00:01:50.745 --> 00:01:52.225
The cakes are good,

00:01:52.305 --> 00:01:54.265
but do you have less sweet ones?

00:01:54.345 --> 00:01:57.265
Do you have keto or stevia cakes?

00:01:57.345 --> 00:02:00.905
I’m watching my weight but I can’t resist.

00:02:01.665 --> 00:02:04.305
We don't have those yet,

00:02:04.385 --> 00:02:06.585
but I'll let you know as soon as we do.

00:02:07.185 --> 00:02:08.425
Thank you.

00:02:08.505 --> 00:02:09.584
You’re welcome.

00:02:12.025 --> 00:02:13.185
Auntie Phailin,

00:02:13.945 --> 00:02:16.545
should I try making less sweet cakes?

00:02:17.345 --> 00:02:19.465
Maybe we can use stevia instead of sugar

00:02:19.545 --> 00:02:21.745
for health-conscious customers.

00:02:22.945 --> 00:02:24.185
Of course.

00:02:24.265 --> 00:02:26.705
I'll give you a free hand to try.

00:02:27.505 --> 00:02:28.425
Thank you.

00:02:57.425 --> 00:02:58.865
That’ll do.

00:03:07.105 --> 00:03:08.225
What are you baking?

00:03:09.145 --> 00:03:10.265
Banana cakes.

00:03:13.745 --> 00:03:14.785
What?

00:03:15.385 --> 00:03:16.905
Who kicked your ass this time?

00:03:16.985 --> 00:03:17.985
Push off.

00:03:31.105 --> 00:03:32.185
DinDin,

00:03:32.265 --> 00:03:34.505
why the hell does this taste crappy?

00:03:36.385 --> 00:03:38.305
Did you change my recipe?

00:03:38.385 --> 00:03:41.905
No, no. It’s the same one.

00:03:41.985 --> 00:03:44.145
I just cut down the sugar
and used stevia instead.

00:03:44.225 --> 00:03:45.345
What for?

00:03:45.425 --> 00:03:47.865
You’d be better spending
your time restocking the display!

00:03:48.385 --> 00:03:50.505
Hey, I’m doing what you said now.

00:03:50.585 --> 00:03:52.305
Always arguing with me, huh?

00:03:52.985 --> 00:03:53.825
Stop! Enough of this!

00:03:54.425 --> 00:03:56.065
Hey, hey! What are you doing?!

00:03:56.145 --> 00:03:57.505
Throw them away!

00:03:57.585 --> 00:03:58.825
Why?

00:03:59.505 --> 00:04:01.145
It’s not up to standard!

00:04:01.225 --> 00:04:03.985
The recipe is still a work in progress.
Just chill out.

00:04:06.785 --> 00:04:09.025
My café is not a lab

00:04:09.825 --> 00:04:12.225
where you can experiment
whenever you feel like it!

00:04:13.185 --> 00:04:14.545
I talked to Auntie Phailin.

00:04:14.625 --> 00:04:16.184
Go talk to her yourself.

00:04:16.265 --> 00:04:18.225
Don’t hide behind my mom.

00:04:18.944 --> 00:04:20.545
When will you stop picking on me?

00:04:21.705 --> 00:04:22.945
I’m being honest!

00:04:23.825 --> 00:04:25.145
Your banana cake is trash!

00:04:25.905 --> 00:04:26.905
That’s it!

00:04:28.425 --> 00:04:30.745
Stop fighting! DinDin! Stop!

00:04:31.705 --> 00:04:34.585
Why can't you two talk like adults?!

00:04:39.225 --> 00:04:40.465
I’m sorry, Auntie Phailin.

00:04:41.625 --> 00:04:43.865
Can't you two just keep this civil?

00:04:43.945 --> 00:04:45.585
About the cakes,

00:04:45.665 --> 00:04:47.945
I allowed DinDin to do it!

00:04:48.025 --> 00:04:49.265
I don't know

00:04:49.345 --> 00:04:52.105
what's going on between you two,

00:04:52.185 --> 00:04:53.905
but while you're at work,

00:04:54.425 --> 00:04:56.585
can you please talk nicely?

00:05:02.465 --> 00:05:04.705
Tawan! Tawan!

00:05:11.025 --> 00:05:12.425
Keep making them.

00:05:12.505 --> 00:05:13.465
Yes.

00:05:23.585 --> 00:05:25.305
-I've taken the lead.
-Oh!

00:05:25.825 --> 00:05:27.865
-Who threw that?
-Pi Doc!

00:05:27.945 --> 00:05:29.025
Come play in the water with me!

00:05:30.905 --> 00:05:33.905
-Whose clip is that?
-Was that your "Pi Doc?"

00:05:34.905 --> 00:05:36.505
How the heck do you know?

00:05:36.585 --> 00:05:38.465
Well, I heard it.

00:05:38.545 --> 00:05:40.185
How far have you guys gone?

00:05:41.025 --> 00:05:43.305
We’re… just talking.

00:05:47.025 --> 00:05:51.025
Hey, do you know how he feels about me?

00:05:51.945 --> 00:05:53.225
Why?

00:05:53.305 --> 00:05:57.745
He told me "I’m cute."

00:05:59.065 --> 00:06:00.985
Does he say that to everyone?

00:06:01.065 --> 00:06:01.985
You think so?

00:06:02.825 --> 00:06:06.105
I doubt he tells everyone they're cute.

00:06:06.865 --> 00:06:09.225
Hey, he’s a psychiatrist.

00:06:09.305 --> 00:06:11.265
He knows what people want to hear.

00:06:11.345 --> 00:06:14.065
Still, the doctor is a busy guy.

00:06:14.145 --> 00:06:18.305
But he invited you for dinner
and a talk. I think he's into you.

00:06:18.385 --> 00:06:21.065
Don’t give him false hope, Lemon.

00:06:21.145 --> 00:06:22.745
Maybe psychiatrists have a way…

00:06:23.265 --> 00:06:26.385
to play mind games?
Have you guys even touched yet?

00:06:29.825 --> 00:06:31.265
What the hell is wrong with you?

00:06:31.345 --> 00:06:32.945
Hey, I’m speaking the truth.

00:06:33.025 --> 00:06:36.425
Alright! Stop rubbing it in!

00:06:37.025 --> 00:06:38.825
I won’t text him.

00:06:46.585 --> 00:06:48.985
Who texted you? Was that the doctor?

00:06:56.225 --> 00:07:01.505
"Are you free tomorrow? I’d love
to show you around Pattaya again."

00:07:01.585 --> 00:07:03.305
There! He likes you!

00:07:03.865 --> 00:07:05.265
He's just being polite.

00:07:16.745 --> 00:07:18.425
WANNA CALL?

00:07:25.065 --> 00:07:26.345
Get out!

00:07:26.425 --> 00:07:28.385
Where are your manners?

00:07:28.465 --> 00:07:30.185
Oh, you…

00:07:30.785 --> 00:07:31.745
Come on, let’s go.

00:07:32.985 --> 00:07:34.305
-Move it.
-Move fast!

00:07:43.185 --> 00:07:45.785
Did you enjoy our bike ride?

00:07:45.865 --> 00:07:49.505
I did, Pi Doc. I felt like…

00:07:50.145 --> 00:07:51.345
I got to see the real Pattaya.

00:07:52.345 --> 00:07:54.025
Since you've been back from the US,

00:07:54.105 --> 00:07:55.585
have you been anywhere with your friends?

00:07:56.385 --> 00:08:01.985
Not really. My friends are gamers,
and I'm not a fan of crowded places.

00:08:02.745 --> 00:08:04.945
And what are you doing right now?

00:08:05.745 --> 00:08:07.665
Packing my things.

00:08:08.785 --> 00:08:12.665
I understand. I've been through
some tough times myself.

00:08:13.465 --> 00:08:15.945
But we'll get through it,
one way or another.

00:08:18.665 --> 00:08:21.225
Are all psychiatrists
such positive thinkers?

00:08:30.665 --> 00:08:31.785
Pi Doc.

00:08:33.465 --> 00:08:34.345
Pi Doc.

00:08:43.065 --> 00:08:44.065
Pi Doc?

00:08:44.144 --> 00:08:45.345
Pi Doc.

00:08:47.025 --> 00:08:47.945
Yes?

00:08:49.745 --> 00:08:50.985
I’m sorry.

00:08:51.785 --> 00:08:53.545
Are you okay?

00:08:55.305 --> 00:08:56.505
I’m fine.

00:08:57.225 --> 00:08:58.985
I was lost in some old memories.

00:09:00.025 --> 00:09:02.665
And… where will you take me tomorrow?

00:09:04.825 --> 00:09:05.825
I'm not telling.

00:09:06.625 --> 00:09:08.185
It's a surprise.

00:09:11.025 --> 00:09:13.385
Alright, see you then.

00:09:14.065 --> 00:09:15.065
Bye-bye.

00:09:17.505 --> 00:09:20.225
Dude, he’s stringing you along.

00:09:20.305 --> 00:09:22.305
Just ask him if he’s seeing anyone.

00:09:22.385 --> 00:09:23.545
Are you nuts?

00:09:24.065 --> 00:09:26.505
Yes, make things clear
so he stops being so vague.

00:10:10.265 --> 00:10:12.545
I haven’t gone cycling with
my family for a long time.

00:10:13.225 --> 00:10:14.705
Why?

00:10:15.985 --> 00:10:16.945
Well…

00:10:18.145 --> 00:10:19.865
I usually went cycling with my family.

00:10:21.145 --> 00:10:25.505
But as everyone grew up
and started working,

00:10:26.625 --> 00:10:28.185
we haven't really done it lately.

00:10:31.225 --> 00:10:35.145
Since I came back,
I haven’t met my dad either.

00:10:36.065 --> 00:10:41.225
He’s my family, but everyone
has their own life. Right, Pi Doc?

00:10:46.545 --> 00:10:49.345
The whole city view is beautiful.

00:11:03.585 --> 00:11:05.585
It would be even better with a lover.

00:11:08.465 --> 00:11:09.945
Bring your girlfriend next time.

00:11:10.905 --> 00:11:13.385
Are you crazy?! I don’t have one!

00:11:13.465 --> 00:11:15.945
I can’t even let people touch me.

00:11:18.865 --> 00:11:20.185
And…

00:11:20.265 --> 00:11:21.345
what about you?

00:11:22.745 --> 00:11:23.865
Do you have one?

00:11:26.985 --> 00:11:28.265
Just broke up with her.

00:11:33.065 --> 00:11:34.065
I’m sorry about that.

00:11:35.625 --> 00:11:36.705
That’s okay.

00:11:37.465 --> 00:11:38.985
I have already moved on.

00:11:39.905 --> 00:11:41.345
That’s kind of quick.

00:11:44.585 --> 00:11:46.305
Why did you two break up?

00:11:52.385 --> 00:11:53.985
I proposed to her.

00:11:57.625 --> 00:11:59.745
And she said she would work in Vietnam.

00:12:01.745 --> 00:12:02.985
So, she denied me.

00:12:06.025 --> 00:12:07.825
I’m not sure if she…

00:12:08.345 --> 00:12:12.865
denied me because of her work
or if we just weren't meant to be.

00:12:14.905 --> 00:12:16.345
I think…

00:12:17.025 --> 00:12:19.345
she didn’t want you to wait for her.

00:12:19.945 --> 00:12:21.465
That’s why.

00:12:25.065 --> 00:12:25.945
I guess so.

00:12:29.705 --> 00:12:33.025
What about you? Never had a girlfriend?

00:12:36.745 --> 00:12:37.945
Yes, I haven’t!

00:12:39.065 --> 00:12:40.705
I’ve never had one.

00:12:43.665 --> 00:12:45.105
With my conditions,

00:12:46.225 --> 00:12:47.945
I’m scared that people won’t…

00:12:50.865 --> 00:12:52.545
accept what I have.

00:12:55.785 --> 00:12:58.665
Sailom, It’s okay to be scared.

00:12:59.345 --> 00:13:01.025
There’s nothing wrong with that.

00:13:02.065 --> 00:13:04.305
Sometimes, it’s better to be scared.

00:13:06.465 --> 00:13:08.865
Fear just makes you more careful

00:13:10.425 --> 00:13:12.785
about starting a relationship.

00:13:13.545 --> 00:13:15.385
Do you really think that way?

00:13:16.985 --> 00:13:18.145
Yes.

00:13:40.465 --> 00:13:45.105
It would be awesome… if more people
go cycling with us. We won’t be lonely.

00:13:49.105 --> 00:13:50.065
How about we start a trip?

00:14:02.465 --> 00:14:06.785
Okay, now we’ll start the drink bidding!

00:14:07.545 --> 00:14:08.985
Number 69, 60 drinks!

00:14:09.065 --> 00:14:11.665
Oh, wow! Our Sky gets 60 drinks--

00:14:11.745 --> 00:14:15.065
-Eighty.
-Eighty drinks! Going once--

00:14:15.145 --> 00:14:16.585
200 drinks!

00:14:16.665 --> 00:14:19.025
And here’s 200 drinks! Going once--

00:14:19.105 --> 00:14:22.545
-210!
-210 drinks! Going once--

00:14:22.625 --> 00:14:25.785
-Make it 299!
-299! Going once!

00:14:25.865 --> 00:14:27.345
Twice--

00:14:27.425 --> 00:14:28.425
350!

00:14:28.505 --> 00:14:32.305
350 drinks! Going once… twice--

00:14:32.385 --> 00:14:33.585
355!

00:14:33.665 --> 00:14:34.945
355 drinks--

00:14:35.025 --> 00:14:38.945
-Make it 400!
-400! Now, it’s 400! Any higher bids?

00:14:39.025 --> 00:14:41.145
Going once… twice…

00:14:41.225 --> 00:14:45.185
And sold! Off you go to the table, Sky!

00:14:45.265 --> 00:14:47.345
Now, he’s off the floor!

00:14:49.105 --> 00:14:50.745
Is all this really necessary?

00:14:50.825 --> 00:14:52.425
For taking me back to my room.

00:14:53.305 --> 00:14:55.385
Did you really have to
compete with Pi Man that much?

00:14:56.185 --> 00:14:58.225
I don't like people touching what's mine.

00:15:05.185 --> 00:15:08.585
Does this mean… I’m yours?

00:15:09.265 --> 00:15:12.505
It means… I just want you
to stay by my side.

00:15:30.625 --> 00:15:31.545
Your reward.

00:15:40.385 --> 00:15:41.585
Surprise!

00:15:41.665 --> 00:15:42.825
Wow!

00:15:43.745 --> 00:15:44.865
What is this?

00:15:45.945 --> 00:15:47.025
Oh!

00:15:50.585 --> 00:15:51.825
What is this?

00:15:52.425 --> 00:15:55.505
The money garland for
the four-kids best mom.

00:15:55.585 --> 00:15:58.905
Oh, does it have to be this grand?

00:15:59.425 --> 00:16:00.945
Is this a Songkran day?

00:16:01.025 --> 00:16:03.505
Actually, I just got my commission.

00:16:03.585 --> 00:16:08.585
I’ve been saving up for 15 days
to help you with the shops rent.

00:16:08.665 --> 00:16:11.625
So nice of you. Thank you.

00:16:11.705 --> 00:16:12.545
Let me hug you.

00:16:15.865 --> 00:16:16.905
So refreshing.

00:16:16.985 --> 00:16:18.745
Now, you’re the favorite son.

00:16:18.825 --> 00:16:20.745
Can I be her favorite one sometime?

00:16:20.825 --> 00:16:24.185
I’m always back home late
and have to work at night.

00:16:24.265 --> 00:16:26.865
Unlike you, you’re always with her.

00:16:27.625 --> 00:16:28.545
That was a sarcastic kiss.

00:16:29.545 --> 00:16:32.785
If Sky is your favorite son,
what about me?

00:16:34.025 --> 00:16:35.545
Aww.

00:16:35.625 --> 00:16:37.945
I love you all equally.

00:16:42.225 --> 00:16:43.625
-Oh, Sky.
-Yes?

00:16:43.705 --> 00:16:46.345
Don’t forget to rest.

00:16:46.425 --> 00:16:50.465
And don’t drink too much booze,
or you’ll get a hard liver.

00:16:50.545 --> 00:16:51.585
Alright.

00:16:51.665 --> 00:16:52.905
Yep, the favorite son.

00:16:52.985 --> 00:16:55.625
Now, Mom lectures you.

00:16:55.705 --> 00:16:59.985
And you. You're not a host,
but you drink day and night.

00:17:00.065 --> 00:17:00.905
Keep lecturing him, Mom.

00:17:00.985 --> 00:17:02.585
Didn’t you lecture him?

00:17:03.305 --> 00:17:04.905
Why does it come back to me?

00:17:07.145 --> 00:17:08.145
How to unwrap these?

00:17:08.224 --> 00:17:12.944
You want to unwrap them? It took me
all day to make the garland this big!

00:17:13.025 --> 00:17:15.265
I must use the money.

00:17:15.345 --> 00:17:18.065
And look, I’ve turned into a lizard!

00:17:18.145 --> 00:17:19.385
I’ll help you unwrap them.

00:17:19.464 --> 00:17:21.545
If I help, can I have a share?

00:17:21.625 --> 00:17:23.704
Hey, stop right there. No.

00:17:23.785 --> 00:17:25.585
-Can I have some?
-No way! You can’t!

00:17:29.585 --> 00:17:30.505
What?

00:17:30.585 --> 00:17:31.865
"A Heart-Healing Trip."

00:17:31.945 --> 00:17:36.385
Just checking in to see who’s up
for a cycling trip to heal the soul.

00:17:37.305 --> 00:17:38.545
What’s this, bro?

00:17:38.625 --> 00:17:40.145
A cycling trip.

00:17:40.225 --> 00:17:41.465
A cycling trip?

00:17:41.545 --> 00:17:42.505
Yep.

00:17:42.585 --> 00:17:43.985
What gets into you?

00:17:44.825 --> 00:17:46.985
I’m thinking of organizing a cycling trip.

00:17:47.065 --> 00:17:52.905
We have a bicycle café. We should invite
people who are interested to join.

00:17:52.985 --> 00:17:54.585
What do you think?

00:17:55.185 --> 00:17:56.265
Good idea.

00:17:56.345 --> 00:17:58.545
I’ll invite customers from my club.

00:17:58.625 --> 00:18:01.785
Good. I’ll invite my patients to join.

00:18:02.385 --> 00:18:05.905
I’m in.
I’ll invite customers from the shop.

00:18:05.985 --> 00:18:09.105
I’ll invite customers from the café.

00:18:09.185 --> 00:18:11.785
-Right, Mom?
-Yes, Sweetie.

00:18:11.865 --> 00:18:12.865
Let’s unwrap this.

00:18:13.985 --> 00:18:15.025
Shall we?

00:18:15.625 --> 00:18:17.585
-Gentle… be careful.
-Mom…

00:18:17.665 --> 00:18:18.985
Can I borrow some?

00:18:20.825 --> 00:18:23.345
It's for Mom!

00:18:39.585 --> 00:18:40.785
Nava.

00:18:43.745 --> 00:18:44.865
How can you come here?

00:18:44.945 --> 00:18:46.225
I’m on a break.

00:18:46.745 --> 00:18:48.905
I saw your story and decided to drop by.

00:18:49.705 --> 00:18:50.745
Are you drunk?

00:18:51.545 --> 00:18:52.385
No.

00:18:52.905 --> 00:18:53.985
Are you sure?

00:18:54.505 --> 00:18:55.385
Not yet.

00:18:55.465 --> 00:18:56.745
You sure?

00:18:59.825 --> 00:19:01.505
Wanna go cycling this Saturday?

00:19:02.345 --> 00:19:06.665
-Cycling?
-My family’s café is organizing a trip.

00:19:09.825 --> 00:19:16.425
I’ve wanted to go on a trip
but… I never got a chance.

00:19:17.025 --> 00:19:18.065
Then come with me.

00:19:18.825 --> 00:19:20.705
-Okay.
-Cheers.

00:19:26.385 --> 00:19:28.745
If you’re free,
please join us on the trip.

00:19:28.825 --> 00:19:31.305
-Sure thing. Thanks for the invite.
-No problem.

00:19:31.385 --> 00:19:33.025
Sounds interesting. Which day?

00:19:33.105 --> 00:19:34.105
This Saturday.

00:19:34.185 --> 00:19:35.025
A HEART HEALING TRIP
COME AND JOIN A BIKE TRIP TOGETHER

00:19:35.105 --> 00:19:37.625
It’s a chill ride to enjoy the view.

00:19:37.705 --> 00:19:39.505
I'll join if I'm free.

00:19:39.585 --> 00:19:41.705
-Sounds interesting!
-Yes, it's intersting!

00:19:45.425 --> 00:19:46.905
Are you guys free?

00:19:46.985 --> 00:19:48.345
Make yourselves free for this.

00:19:48.425 --> 00:19:50.905
It's the "Heart-Healing Trip."

00:19:51.785 --> 00:19:54.665
Over 50 people have signed up.
I'm organizing it.

00:19:55.185 --> 00:19:57.225
So, come join us if you can.

00:19:57.305 --> 00:19:59.225
That's good. It sounds interesting.

00:19:59.305 --> 00:20:03.345
I haven't cycled in ages.
I'll need to warm up.

00:20:04.625 --> 00:20:06.465
Alright, are we ready?

00:20:06.545 --> 00:20:10.985
If you don’t have any plans,
come cycling with us this Saturday.

00:20:14.345 --> 00:20:15.865
Do you think you can handle the ride?

00:20:15.945 --> 00:20:17.345
Of course!

00:20:19.105 --> 00:20:19.945
‎Alright!

00:20:20.025 --> 00:20:20.945
Wooh!

00:20:30.505 --> 00:20:33.665
Damn, Pi Nabnueng!
Tons of people are interested.

00:20:33.745 --> 00:20:35.505
Look at all these sign-ups.

00:20:35.585 --> 00:20:38.225
-Of course.
-You’re the man, Bro.

00:20:40.065 --> 00:20:43.105
Hey, we haven’t
hung out like this in ages.

00:20:43.185 --> 00:20:46.465
-Let’s have a toast!
-What are we waiting for?

00:20:50.105 --> 00:20:53.625
-Hey, Bro. About this trip…
-Yes?

00:20:53.705 --> 00:20:55.385
you do this to…

00:20:55.465 --> 00:21:00.825
heal your own heart?

00:21:00.905 --> 00:21:06.025
Yeah, you’ve been looking stressed.
Can you really move on from Yanin?

00:21:09.785 --> 00:21:12.705
-I can.
-What?! With who? Tell me!

00:21:12.785 --> 00:21:14.705
-That’s quick.
-Hey,

00:21:15.305 --> 00:21:16.665
does it have to be someone?

00:21:16.745 --> 00:21:18.225
I’m working!

00:21:18.305 --> 00:21:19.705
Haven’t you heard?

00:21:20.425 --> 00:21:21.465
"Just focus on work."

00:21:21.545 --> 00:21:23.545
-Aww…
-Yeah, work…

00:21:23.625 --> 00:21:25.305
-But Looksoh said…
-What?

00:21:25.385 --> 00:21:26.865
you went cycling with an American guy.

00:21:28.105 --> 00:21:30.345
What guy? No, you’re wrong!

00:21:30.425 --> 00:21:31.425
Are you sure?

00:21:33.025 --> 00:21:34.505
He's just a kid!

00:21:35.265 --> 00:21:36.385
I see…

00:21:37.705 --> 00:21:39.265
Who is that kid?

00:21:40.225 --> 00:21:41.385
His name is Sailom.

00:21:41.465 --> 00:21:42.745
He’s just a kid.

00:21:43.345 --> 00:21:44.425
But he has…

00:21:45.465 --> 00:21:46.345
a condition.

00:21:47.425 --> 00:21:49.425
Haphephobia.

00:21:49.505 --> 00:21:50.985
You can’t touch him like this.

00:21:51.065 --> 00:21:52.425
-No touching?
-Yep.

00:21:52.505 --> 00:21:53.785
How can you date him?

00:21:55.825 --> 00:21:57.345
I…

00:21:57.865 --> 00:21:59.585
I must… treat him first.

00:22:00.345 --> 00:22:02.705
Ah, so if you…

00:22:02.785 --> 00:22:05.705
If you date him,

00:22:05.785 --> 00:22:09.265
do you have to keep your distance
like this when you have sex with him?

00:22:09.785 --> 00:22:10.625
‎-Wait!
‎-Come on!

00:22:11.585 --> 00:22:15.545
That would hurt like hell
if you hit there. Sorry. Just teasing.

00:22:17.145 --> 00:22:18.905
You were so bold.

00:22:18.985 --> 00:22:21.185
I know. I was teasing him.

00:22:21.265 --> 00:22:22.505
What about you?!

00:22:23.025 --> 00:22:25.665
-Look at him deflecting.
-Yeah.

00:22:26.945 --> 00:22:29.265
Got someone yet?
You’ve been awfully quiet lately.

00:22:29.345 --> 00:22:32.185
Yeah, What's the deal? Spill it.

00:22:34.265 --> 00:22:37.145
I fix bicycles.
I don’t have time for that.

00:22:40.105 --> 00:22:44.145
What about… your favorite little brother?

00:22:45.465 --> 00:22:48.265
Hardly stays home.
Probably gets clingy with a customer.

00:22:48.345 --> 00:22:51.425
What? No, I don’t have anyone!

00:22:51.505 --> 00:22:54.665
I never get attached to customers, Bro.

00:22:54.745 --> 00:22:56.065
They get attached to me.

00:22:56.145 --> 00:22:57.385
Woah!

00:22:58.705 --> 00:22:59.945
So cool!

00:23:00.025 --> 00:23:02.265
Total Sigma Male energy!

00:23:04.585 --> 00:23:06.545
-Damn, I’m proud of you.
-No doubt!

00:23:06.625 --> 00:23:08.065
Awesome.

00:23:08.145 --> 00:23:09.425
Damn!

00:23:09.945 --> 00:23:11.185
But seriously…

00:23:14.265 --> 00:23:16.345
I want to quit being a host.

00:23:17.025 --> 00:23:17.905
Quit?

00:23:17.985 --> 00:23:19.625
-Uh-huh
-Why?

00:23:23.345 --> 00:23:24.545
I feel like…

00:23:25.065 --> 00:23:29.625
I'm getting too
emotionally involved lately.

00:23:29.705 --> 00:23:32.225
But deep down, in reality…

00:23:32.825 --> 00:23:36.025
There's no way we could
ever have a real relationship.

00:23:38.945 --> 00:23:40.745
You get what I mean?

00:23:41.345 --> 00:23:42.385
Are you even listening?

00:23:48.345 --> 00:23:49.385
Oh, come on.

00:24:02.585 --> 00:24:04.665
Still better than feeling
something but pretending you don't.

00:24:13.705 --> 00:24:15.145
He's acting weird.

00:24:15.665 --> 00:24:16.825
Big time.

00:24:22.545 --> 00:24:24.025
The hell is weird? Cheers!

00:24:24.105 --> 00:24:25.385
-Cheers!
-Cheers!

00:24:25.465 --> 00:24:27.985
Nice dodge. I'll let it slide for now.

00:24:33.585 --> 00:24:35.065
Are you serious about quitting?

00:24:35.665 --> 00:24:37.145
Of course!

00:24:37.225 --> 00:24:39.305
-He’s just drunk.
-Hey, Bro!

00:24:39.385 --> 00:24:41.785
The money is great, but…

00:24:42.305 --> 00:24:43.865
I don’t want to do this forever.

00:24:44.825 --> 00:24:48.225
-Obsess with a customer, for sure.
-Customer…

00:24:48.305 --> 00:24:52.745
My ass! I’m not attached to them.
They’re attached to me.

00:24:52.825 --> 00:24:53.665
Roger that!

00:24:59.305 --> 00:25:03.865
BRING YOUR FRIENDS ALONG TOO.

00:25:05.305 --> 00:25:06.865
SURE THING, PI DOC.

00:25:08.025 --> 00:25:10.705
Wow, look at that grin.

00:25:10.785 --> 00:25:13.065
Is it your Pi Doc again?

00:25:13.585 --> 00:25:17.545
Yeah, you're so nosy.
Anyway, come cycling with me.

00:25:18.385 --> 00:25:19.225
Cycling?

00:25:19.825 --> 00:25:20.865
Yep.

00:25:21.505 --> 00:25:23.705
It's Pi Doc’s cycling trip.

00:25:24.225 --> 00:25:25.625
I already signed you up.

00:25:27.065 --> 00:25:30.105
Are you kidding? Do I look like a cyclist?

00:25:30.185 --> 00:25:32.185
Guys, give me a hand.

00:25:36.705 --> 00:25:38.225
Why did you buy so much stuff?

00:25:38.825 --> 00:25:40.785
Oh, like you eat any less.

00:25:40.865 --> 00:25:44.065
We're eating at home for your safety.
So you don't have to bump into anyone.

00:25:45.385 --> 00:25:47.345
-What about the ice?
-Go get it yourself.

00:25:47.425 --> 00:25:48.865
Hey, I'm playing a game now.

00:25:49.705 --> 00:25:50.825
Look at this guy!

00:25:51.425 --> 00:25:53.705
-I’m chatting with Pi Doc.
-I'm playing my game.

00:25:58.945 --> 00:26:01.465
-Cheers! Yay!
-Yay!

00:26:09.265 --> 00:26:11.505
So, Sailom…

00:26:12.025 --> 00:26:13.465
have you slept with him yet?

00:26:13.545 --> 00:26:14.945
Are you crazy?!

00:26:15.505 --> 00:26:19.225
When would I even have the chance?
Look at my condition.

00:26:19.305 --> 00:26:24.385
Ever thought? If you weren't like this,
you might've already been his boyfriend.

00:26:27.825 --> 00:26:29.025
I have.

00:26:30.425 --> 00:26:32.785
But I don't know how he feels about me.

00:26:34.305 --> 00:26:36.425
Why don't you just ask him straight out?

00:26:38.425 --> 00:26:40.745
If he doesn't feel the same,

00:26:41.305 --> 00:26:42.505
I'll just look like a fool.

00:26:43.385 --> 00:26:44.345
True.

00:26:45.185 --> 00:26:48.305
But I think you need to get cured first.

00:26:48.385 --> 00:26:53.865
Otherwise, you won't be happy
even if you date him. Right?

00:26:55.305 --> 00:26:58.705
Yeah. If you can't touch
each other, how's it gonna work?

00:26:59.385 --> 00:27:02.745
-How are you guys gonna have sex?
-What the hell are you talking about?

00:27:02.825 --> 00:27:04.545
Am I lying, though?

00:27:08.785 --> 00:27:09.745
Fine.

00:27:10.505 --> 00:27:13.545
How am I supposed to get cured?

00:27:15.425 --> 00:27:18.145
Didn’t you tell me he's a psychiatrist?

00:27:18.745 --> 00:27:22.345
Get the treatment and get the guy.

00:27:23.945 --> 00:27:24.945
Good point.

00:27:27.105 --> 00:27:29.065
Hey, you guys…

00:27:30.825 --> 00:27:31.945
Cheers!

00:27:32.025 --> 00:27:34.425
-Cheers!
-Yay!

00:28:14.145 --> 00:28:15.185
Sailom!

00:28:23.385 --> 00:28:25.065
What are you doing here?

00:29:20.945 --> 00:29:21.905
Sailom.

00:29:22.505 --> 00:29:23.625
Sailom…

00:29:29.905 --> 00:29:30.865
Sailom!

00:29:33.705 --> 00:29:34.705
Yes?

00:29:36.025 --> 00:29:37.385
Are you daydreaming?

00:29:38.105 --> 00:29:39.185
You even did a "kiss-kiss" face.

00:29:41.065 --> 00:29:43.385
I was thinking about eating strawberries.

00:29:43.465 --> 00:29:44.985
Strawberries.

00:29:45.065 --> 00:29:46.265
Kiss-kiss.

00:29:48.785 --> 00:29:50.865
Shall we get started?

00:29:53.305 --> 00:29:55.905
What made you decide
to seek treatment with me?

00:29:57.665 --> 00:29:59.385
My friends motivated me.

00:30:00.545 --> 00:30:03.625
And I really want to get
cured from this condition.

00:30:06.345 --> 00:30:08.745
I know it won't be easy,

00:30:08.825 --> 00:30:10.745
and I'm scared.

00:30:12.065 --> 00:30:12.905
But…

00:30:13.425 --> 00:30:15.505
I don't want to feel this way anymore.

00:30:16.985 --> 00:30:19.145
And what about the cycling trip?

00:30:19.905 --> 00:30:21.145
Have you invited your friends yet?

00:30:22.385 --> 00:30:23.505
I have.

00:30:24.065 --> 00:30:26.345
Lemon and James are dying to join.

00:30:26.425 --> 00:30:31.465
We're already looking for
a place to practice our riding.

00:30:32.385 --> 00:30:34.945
Great. You won't get
too tired on the big day.

00:30:35.945 --> 00:30:38.305
It's going to be very sunny that day.

00:30:42.265 --> 00:30:45.505
Don't forget to wear sunscreen,
so you don't get burned.

00:30:45.585 --> 00:30:47.185
This is for you.

00:30:49.505 --> 00:30:50.585
Thanks.

00:30:51.105 --> 00:30:53.705
So, what did you do today?
Tell me about it.

00:30:54.665 --> 00:30:56.905
Nothing much, really.

00:30:58.465 --> 00:31:02.425
Oh, seeing you is the highlight of my day.

00:31:04.625 --> 00:31:08.305
Uh… I mean, because
I don't get to visit the clinic often.

00:31:14.145 --> 00:31:14.985
Sailom.

00:31:16.265 --> 00:31:17.425
Yes?

00:31:25.265 --> 00:31:26.905
Hello, Mr. Sailom.

00:31:27.865 --> 00:31:34.025
I’m Doctor Ying. I’ll be taking over
your case from today on.

00:31:35.865 --> 00:31:36.825
Right…

00:31:37.425 --> 00:31:39.185
How are you doing today?

00:31:41.425 --> 00:31:42.625
I’m fine…

00:31:42.705 --> 00:31:46.705
And… did you sleep well last night?

00:31:48.345 --> 00:31:49.265
Pretty good…

00:31:49.785 --> 00:31:53.025
What did you have
for breakfast this morning?

00:31:55.545 --> 00:31:57.505
Just some coffee and a sandwich.

00:31:57.585 --> 00:31:58.825
I see.

00:32:00.905 --> 00:32:04.785
According to your records,
you’re studying abroad, right?

00:32:07.545 --> 00:32:08.665
Yes…

00:32:09.345 --> 00:32:10.825
I'm studying in the States.

00:32:12.385 --> 00:32:14.945
It's summer break now,
so I'm back to stay with my dad.

00:32:16.425 --> 00:32:18.065
Staying with your father?

00:32:20.305 --> 00:32:23.185
So, are you originally from Pattaya?

00:32:24.705 --> 00:32:26.065
Sailom…

00:32:28.185 --> 00:32:31.305
-This is our new home, Sweetie.
-Yes, Mom.

00:32:31.385 --> 00:32:33.625
Oh, you're finally here.

00:32:37.265 --> 00:32:38.665
Say hello to him, Dear.

00:32:39.185 --> 00:32:40.465
Hello, Sir.

00:32:40.545 --> 00:32:41.785
Welcome home, Son.

00:32:41.865 --> 00:32:45.265
From now on, we're one big family.

00:32:45.865 --> 00:32:46.905
Yes, Sir.

00:32:56.185 --> 00:32:57.505
Eat up, Son.

00:32:59.425 --> 00:33:01.185
So you can grow up strong.

00:33:15.825 --> 00:33:17.745
You can always tell me
if you have problems.

00:33:54.545 --> 00:33:56.825
Don't you dare tell anyone about this.

00:33:58.105 --> 00:34:00.265
Or I'll kill your mother.

00:34:52.065 --> 00:34:55.585
I will teach you.

00:36:04.785 --> 00:36:05.945
Sailom…

00:36:07.985 --> 00:36:09.345
where are you, Son?

00:36:10.425 --> 00:36:12.705
You’re quite good at hiding.

00:36:16.425 --> 00:36:18.345
If I catch you…

00:36:19.225 --> 00:36:21.105
you’re going to be punished, Son.

00:36:27.465 --> 00:36:29.945
Could you be right…

00:36:53.625 --> 00:36:54.825
What's wrong with you?

00:37:03.305 --> 00:37:04.785
…Here?!

00:37:04.865 --> 00:37:06.145
There you are!

00:37:06.225 --> 00:37:11.505
-Don’t squirm! Come on! Get out!
-Let me go! Let go of me!

00:37:17.345 --> 00:37:18.625
Ying…

00:37:19.385 --> 00:37:20.225
where's Sailom?

00:37:20.745 --> 00:37:22.665
He left a little while ago.

00:37:25.265 --> 00:37:26.545
Look…

00:37:26.625 --> 00:37:28.785
he doesn't seem ready at all.

00:37:33.385 --> 00:37:35.505
Is something bothering you? Or…

00:37:36.505 --> 00:37:37.465
do you want to take over this case?

00:37:38.385 --> 00:37:42.505
No, don't worry about it.
I asked for your help with this one.

00:37:42.585 --> 00:37:44.825
It’s best if you handle it.

00:37:48.265 --> 00:37:49.105
‎Uh-huh.

00:37:52.465 --> 00:37:56.185
Oh, I have an errand to run. Gotta go.

00:37:56.705 --> 00:37:58.305
See you later.

00:38:21.345 --> 00:38:22.705
Hello?

00:38:22.785 --> 00:38:23.905
Phailin?

00:38:24.425 --> 00:38:25.825
This is Lada.

00:38:27.905 --> 00:38:30.225
How is Nabnueng doing?

00:38:34.145 --> 00:38:35.305
You've got the wrong number.

00:39:29.345 --> 00:39:30.425
Were you sleeping?

00:39:32.305 --> 00:39:33.145
Uh-huh?

00:39:33.225 --> 00:39:35.025
Sleeping on the job, are you?

00:39:36.385 --> 00:39:38.185
Just resting my eyes.

00:39:38.985 --> 00:39:41.785
The cookies need to
cool down before packing.

00:39:42.825 --> 00:39:44.585
Do you even know anything about baking?

00:39:45.105 --> 00:39:46.185
You were asleep.

00:39:52.145 --> 00:39:53.785
Yeah, I was.

00:39:54.705 --> 00:39:55.865
So what?

00:39:56.985 --> 00:39:58.105
That's it.

00:39:59.185 --> 00:40:00.785
I hired you,

00:40:01.305 --> 00:40:03.265
but you’re sleeping during working hours?

00:40:04.425 --> 00:40:06.145
I’m docking your pay.

00:40:06.225 --> 00:40:08.865
You're a terrible example for the others.

00:40:10.745 --> 00:40:12.505
Whoa, whoa. Hey…

00:40:13.025 --> 00:40:14.585
Calm down, man.

00:40:15.185 --> 00:40:17.745
Calm down? You’re sleeping.

00:40:18.265 --> 00:40:19.625
You can punch me.

00:40:20.145 --> 00:40:21.785
Just don't touch my salary.

00:40:22.385 --> 00:40:24.265
I don't even have enough to get by.

00:40:25.865 --> 00:40:29.065
Hit me. Just hit me. Right here.

00:40:30.105 --> 00:40:31.465
Then we’ll be even.

00:40:31.545 --> 00:40:35.505
-Let go of me!
-I said punch me!

00:40:37.705 --> 00:40:40.185
Just don't touch my salary!

00:41:16.385 --> 00:41:17.705
Pi DinDin,

00:41:21.465 --> 00:41:22.705
are you okay?

00:41:25.385 --> 00:41:26.465
I'm fine.

00:41:26.545 --> 00:41:29.545
Take it easy. Don't take
Pi Tawan's words too seriously.

00:41:29.625 --> 00:41:32.865
He won't actually cut
your pay. It's an empty threat.

00:41:32.945 --> 00:41:36.265
He's got a sharp tongue,
but a kind heart. Right, Mickey?

00:41:36.785 --> 00:41:40.985
Yeah, that's just how he is.
Don't stress out, Pi DinDin.

00:41:43.785 --> 00:41:45.185
Okay.

00:42:07.265 --> 00:42:09.345
-Hello, Pi Man.
-Hey.

00:42:14.225 --> 00:42:16.425
-Let’s have a drink.
-Alright.

00:42:19.585 --> 00:42:20.705
I’ll pour it for you.

00:42:20.785 --> 00:42:23.905
It’s okay. I’ll do it myself.

00:42:27.345 --> 00:42:28.545
Here’s yours.

00:42:30.505 --> 00:42:31.705
You like it strong.

00:42:33.225 --> 00:42:35.265
-Cheers!
-Cheers!

00:42:38.825 --> 00:42:41.185
I thought you wouldn’t come.
I saw you were taking a break.

00:42:42.065 --> 00:42:46.305
You booked me for the whole night.
Of course, I had to come.

00:42:48.305 --> 00:42:51.385
I missed you, Sky.
Come stay at my place tonight.

00:42:52.185 --> 00:42:56.385
Whoa, Pi Man.
You’re not gonna let me go home?

00:42:56.905 --> 00:43:01.545
What? You’ve stayed over before.
Why do you want to go home?

00:43:05.785 --> 00:43:07.585
-It's just…
-Why?

00:43:08.465 --> 00:43:10.105
You don't want to be with me anymore?

00:43:11.625 --> 00:43:12.825
It’s not like that--

00:43:12.905 --> 00:43:13.985
Of course,

00:43:14.665 --> 00:43:16.145
you don’t want to.

00:43:16.225 --> 00:43:19.465
If I didn't care about you,
why would I be here all night?

00:43:19.545 --> 00:43:20.465
Cheers to that.

00:43:30.705 --> 00:43:31.705
Sky…

00:43:32.705 --> 00:43:33.545
I thought you were taking a break.

00:43:35.665 --> 00:43:36.745
Nava…

00:43:39.585 --> 00:43:41.265
Pi Man booked me for the whole night.

00:43:43.985 --> 00:43:46.065
Can I help you? This is my table.

00:43:48.025 --> 00:43:50.345
My bad. I’m here say hi to Sky.

00:43:51.585 --> 00:43:54.385
Where are your manners?
I paid for his time tonight!

00:43:55.945 --> 00:43:57.105
So?

00:43:57.185 --> 00:43:59.985
I can't say hi to my friend?

00:44:01.465 --> 00:44:02.385
Are you looking for trouble?

00:44:03.665 --> 00:44:04.625
No, I’m not.

00:44:06.585 --> 00:44:09.745
When you booked him,
did I ever get in your way?

00:44:13.905 --> 00:44:17.145
-Sky, is that your glass?
-Yeah.

00:44:29.385 --> 00:44:30.265
That's enough!

00:44:34.065 --> 00:44:35.825
Hey! Nava, stop!

00:44:36.345 --> 00:44:38.825
I said stop!

00:44:39.585 --> 00:44:40.505
Stop!

00:44:43.465 --> 00:44:45.225
Pi Man, please calm down.

00:44:46.385 --> 00:44:48.385
-Let's go, Nava.
-Where are you going?!

00:44:48.905 --> 00:44:50.905
Stay with me! Let him go!

00:44:52.105 --> 00:44:53.425
Hey, stop!

00:44:53.505 --> 00:44:55.625
-Ah!
-Let go of me!

00:44:55.705 --> 00:44:56.705
Mr. Man!

00:44:56.785 --> 00:44:59.065
Security! Get him out of here! Now!

00:44:59.145 --> 00:45:00.665
Please calm down, Mr. Man.

00:45:00.745 --> 00:45:02.505
-We’re so sorry.
-I’m so sorry, Mama.

00:45:02.585 --> 00:45:04.945
-Take care of him.
-Pi Man, take it easy.

00:45:05.025 --> 00:45:08.225
Did you see him?!
He was trying to screw with me!

00:45:08.745 --> 00:45:10.345
Why didn't you stand up for me?

00:45:10.945 --> 00:45:13.305
Look at me. I'm right here with you.

00:45:13.865 --> 00:45:16.425
Please calm down.
Let's go back and have fun.

00:45:16.505 --> 00:45:18.305
Hey! Nothing to see here!
Keep the party going!

00:45:18.385 --> 00:45:21.345
Let's just go back and have fun, okay?

00:45:22.425 --> 00:45:24.505
Let me fill your glass.

00:45:25.145 --> 00:45:27.945
I'll even go back to your room tonight.

00:45:28.025 --> 00:45:31.225
You're out of drinks.
Let me get you another one.

00:45:32.225 --> 00:45:33.425
Hey!

00:46:45.105 --> 00:46:47.265
What the hell do you want from me now?

00:46:47.345 --> 00:46:49.065
-Someone to drink with.
-I'm not drinking.

00:46:49.665 --> 00:46:52.065
Tawan might act tough on the outside,

00:46:52.145 --> 00:46:54.905
but he’s actually a very kind person.

00:46:56.025 --> 00:46:57.505
I'm thinking about quitting the host job.

00:46:57.585 --> 00:46:58.505
Why?

00:47:00.665 --> 00:47:02.745
What's wrong?
You've been spacing out all morning.

00:47:02.825 --> 00:47:05.545
Can you tell me what's going on?

00:47:05.625 --> 00:47:07.465
Why did you decide to stop the treatment?

00:47:07.545 --> 00:47:10.465
If this treatment is like
riding a bike, just like you said.

00:47:10.545 --> 00:47:13.465
Now, you’ve cycled
far away and left me behind.